1
00:00:06,640 --> 00:00:07,920
Xixi, be careful.

2
00:00:11,680 --> 00:00:13,520
Slow down. Don't run so fast.

3
00:00:15,240 --> 00:00:15,920
Honey,

4
00:00:16,600 --> 00:00:17,660
let's have a drink.

5
00:00:19,120 --> 00:00:20,480
I haven't had a drink in ages.

6
00:00:20,480 --> 00:00:21,840
I get drunk so easily.

7
00:00:23,480 --> 00:00:24,280
Honey,

8
00:00:25,600 --> 00:00:27,400
we finally have some alone time.

9
00:00:28,000 --> 00:00:29,400
Just have a drink with me.

10
00:00:32,000 --> 00:00:32,840
Alright.

11
00:00:52,600 --> 00:00:53,240
Honey,

12
00:00:54,240 --> 00:00:56,040
your sandwiches are the best.

13
00:00:56,640 --> 00:00:57,520
Have one.

14
00:00:58,200 --> 00:00:58,840
Okay.

15
00:01:14,440 --> 00:01:15,480
Honey,

16
00:01:15,640 --> 00:01:18,000
why don't I go with you

17
00:01:18,640 --> 00:01:19,440
for a walk?

18
00:01:20,200 --> 00:01:21,000
A stroll

19
00:01:21,640 --> 00:01:23,170
might make you feel better.

20
00:02:31,520 --> 00:02:34,079
Is anyone there? Please save my wife!

21
00:02:37,440 --> 00:02:38,240
Honey,

22
00:02:38,840 --> 00:02:39,680
don't worry.

23
00:02:40,680 --> 00:02:42,480
I'm coming to save you right now.

24
00:02:46,520 --> 00:02:48,440
I love the sandwiches you make.

25
00:02:48,760 --> 00:02:49,480
Really?

26
00:02:49,480 --> 00:02:50,610
Xixi loves them too.

27
00:02:50,680 --> 00:02:52,680
We can take them on our picnic later.

28
00:02:58,240 --> 00:02:59,440
You look so handsome.

29
00:02:59,880 --> 00:03:00,880
I don't want to go to work.

30
00:03:00,880 --> 00:03:01,940
I hate leaving you.

31
00:03:02,360 --> 00:03:03,800
I hate leaving you too.

32
00:03:03,800 --> 00:03:05,880
But everyone is waiting for your meeting.

33
00:03:05,880 --> 00:03:06,680
Come with me.

34
00:03:06,840 --> 00:03:07,680
Why would I go with you?

35
00:03:07,680 --> 00:03:08,640
Go to work.

36
00:03:09,120 --> 00:03:10,080
Crazy.

37
00:03:10,240 --> 00:03:11,640
Actually, I was at the hotel that day.

38
00:03:11,640 --> 00:03:13,080
I heard your husband and his mistress

39
00:03:13,080 --> 00:03:14,210
plotting to kill you

40
00:03:14,400 --> 00:03:16,079
to get a huge payout.

41
00:03:16,760 --> 00:03:18,890
Do you still want to save your husband?

42
00:03:27,440 --> 00:03:28,240
Yes.

43
00:03:30,079 --> 00:03:32,140
Changing destiny comes with a price.

44
00:03:33,040 --> 00:03:35,300
Besides, my daughter is still in the car.

45
00:04:37,040 --> 00:04:37,800
It's you.

46
00:04:38,920 --> 00:04:39,980
How could it be you?

47
00:04:43,040 --> 00:04:44,170
Honey, are you okay?

48
00:04:49,840 --> 00:04:51,440
Thank you for saving my wife.

49
00:04:53,360 --> 00:04:54,159
It's nothing.

50
00:04:54,400 --> 00:04:55,600
I was just being nosy.

51
00:05:18,560 --> 00:05:22,600
Xixi, Xixi, Xixi.

52
00:05:23,200 --> 00:05:24,000
Xixi.

53
00:05:28,440 --> 00:05:30,880
Mom.

54
00:05:42,760 --> 00:05:44,600
Xixi.

55
00:05:49,680 --> 00:05:52,120
My Xixi.

56
00:06:53,440 --> 00:06:55,800
Honey, I missed you so much.

57
00:06:58,240 --> 00:06:59,370
I just took a shower.

58
00:06:59,400 --> 00:07:00,200
Smells good.

59
00:07:03,480 --> 00:07:04,680
What's wrong, honey?

60
00:07:07,080 --> 00:07:07,880
Nothing.

61
00:07:08,400 --> 00:07:09,530
I just took a shower.

62
00:07:09,720 --> 00:07:10,680
I'm all wet.

63
00:07:13,240 --> 00:07:14,040
It's okay.

64
00:07:22,480 --> 00:07:23,560
Honey,

65
00:07:24,840 --> 00:07:26,200
I had a nightmare.

66
00:07:29,000 --> 00:07:30,200
Don't worry about it.

67
00:07:30,920 --> 00:07:32,380
Everyone has nightmares.

68
00:07:34,680 --> 00:07:35,480
Yeah.

69
00:07:37,040 --> 00:07:38,500
Everyone has nightmares.

70
00:07:40,720 --> 00:07:43,760
Your nightmare begins now.
